name: Precious Lord
comments: Re-recorded live in 1972 for the classic Amazing Grace album. The re-recording took place at the New Temple Missionary Baptist Church in Los Angeles, California, with James Cleveland & The Southern California Community Choir as part of a medley with a song called You've Got a Friend in Jesus. Despite the label credits, the second part of the medley is not a cover of You've Got a Friend .
